BEGIN_PGML A group of college students were asked about their TV watching habits. Of those surveyed, 28 students watch _The Walking Dead_, 19 watch _The Blacklist_, and 24 watch _Game of Thrones_. Additionally, 16 watch _The Walking Dead_ and _The Blacklist_, 14 watch _The Walking Dead_ and _Game of Thrones_, and 10 watch _The Blacklist_ and _Game of Thrones_. There are 8 students who watch all three shows. How many students surveyed watched at least one of the shows?
[_____]{39}
