####################################### ### Generated from PreTeXt source ### on 2018-07-31T08:07:44-06:00 ### ### http://mathbook.pugetsound.edu ### ####################################### ## DBsubject() ## DBchapter() ## DBsection() ## Level() ## KEYWORDS() ## TitleText1(Discrete Mathematics) ## EditionText1() ## AuthorText1(Oscar Levin) ## Section1(not reported) ## Problem1(1.2.4) ## Author() ## Institution() ## Language(en-US)
