############################################################ # Body ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML How many anagrams are there of the word "assesses" that start with the letter "a"?
[_____]{$ans}
END_PGML
############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION After the first letter (a), we must rearrange the remaining 7 letters. There are only two letters (s and e), so this is really just a bit-string question (think of s as 1 and e as 0). Thus there [`{7 \choose 2} = 21`] anagrams starting with "a".
END_PGML_SOLUTION
