####################################### ### Generated from PreTeXt source ### on 2018-07-31T08:07:45-06:00 ### ### http://mathbook.pugetsound.edu ### ####################################### ## DBsubject() ## DBchapter() ## DBsection() ## Level() ## KEYWORDS() ## TitleText1(Discrete Mathematics) ## EditionText1() ## AuthorText1(Oscar Levin) ## Section1(not reported) ## Problem1(3.1.5) ## Author() ## Institution() ## Language(en-US)
DOCUMENT();
############################################################ # Load Macros ############################################################ loadMacros( "PGstandard.pl", "MathObjects.pl", "PGML.pl", "AnswerFormatHelp.pl", "parserPopUp.pl", "PGcourse.pl", );
############################################################ # Header ############################################################ COMMENT('Authored in PreTeXt'); TEXT(beginproblem());
############################################################ # PG Setup ############################################################ Context('Numeric'); $converse = PopUp( ["?","Converse","Contrapositive","Neither"], "Converse", # correct answer ); $contrapositive = PopUp( ["?","Converse","Contrapositive","Neither"], "Contrapositive", # correct answer ); $neither = PopUp( ["?","Converse","Contrapositive","Neither"], "Neither", # correct answer );
############################################################ # Body ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML Consider the statement, "If you will give me a cow, then I will give you magic beans." Decide whether each statement below is the converse, the contrapositive, or neither. a. If you will give me a cow, then I will not give you magic beans. [_____]{$neither}
a. If I will not give you magic beans, then you will not give me a cow. [_____]{$contrapositive}
a. If I will give you magic beans, then you will give me a cow. [_____]{$converse}
a. If you will not give me a cow, then I will not give you magic beans. [_____]{$neither}
a. You will give me a cow and I will not give you magic beans. [_____]{$neither}
a. If I will give you magic beans, then you will not give me a cow. [_____]{$neither}
END_PGML
############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION The converse is "If I will give you magic beans, then you will give me a cow." The contrapositive is "If I will not give you magic beans, then you will not give me a cow." All the other statements are neither the converse nor contrapositive.
END_PGML_SOLUTION
############################################################ # End Problem ############################################################
